    <h2>Rehabilitation starts with you</h2>
    <p>Our goal is to provide healthcare professionals and the average person access to easy to understand exercises that can aid
        with the rehabilitation process during injury. Our database contains over 100+ exercises catered to providing the appropriate
        level of care required for any stage during injury.
    </p>
    <h3>How it works</h3>
    <p>This site was designed to give easy to access exercises commonly used in physiotherapy practice
        to help strengthen specific areas of injury. Just simply click the area of interest and choose 
        any of the exercises that interest you. Each exercise is given a level of difficulty and will 
        have indication when it is best to perform at which stage of recovery.
    </p>
